      "canonical_label": "Contagonist",
      "dynamic_pair_id": null,
      "encoding_hint": "A concept unique to Dramatica, the Contagonist is the character that balances the Guardian. If Protagonist and Antagonist can archetypically be thought of as \"Good\" versus \"Evil,\" the Contagonist is \"Temptation\" to the Guardian's \"Conscience.\" Because the Contagonist",
