      "canonical_label": "Emotion",
      "dynamic_pair_id": null,
      "encoding_hint": "The Emotional Archetypal Character reacts passionately to turns of events without considering the consequences or best course to achieve his purpose. Frequently portrayed as a \"screamer\" or \"big dumb ox\" this character is really not stupid.",
